n: Healthy Frozen Fruit Cups: A Dessert You Feel Good Not Guilty About.
des: "The idea came from a family recipe for fruit cups that was amazing but not healthy at all. So getting my inspiration from paleo banana ice cream, I made a healthy version. Enjoy as a side or dessert!"
ins:
Line 6 muffin cups with paper liners.
Mix mashed bananas and milk together in a bowl; fold in orange slices. Pour mixture into the prepared muffin cups. Freeze until solid, at least 1 hour. Defrost for about 10 minutes before serving.
